        "message": "LU-10398 osd: undo partially written data\n\nosd_ldiskfs_write_rec() writes data by pages and may\nexit with partially written data causing data corruption,\nespecially in llog case.\nUndo partially written data truncating it back.\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <mike.pershin@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I86e4f0cd10945e2a8cccf513e8b98245f36a6a46\n"
